parts.text:
**Asian**

**Soups:**

* Miso soup (Japanese)
* Tom yum soup (Thai)
* Pho (Vietnamese)
* Tantanmen (Chinese)
* Laksa (Malaysian)

**Stews:**

* Beef rendang (Indonesian)
* Chicken tikka masala (Indian)
* Japanese curry
* Korean beef stew (galbi jjim)
* Massaman curry (Thai)

**Hot Drinks:**

* Matcha latte (Japanese)
* Chinese tea (e.g., pu'erh, oolong)
* Thai iced tea
* Vietnamese iced coffee
* Ginger tea

**Mediterranean**

**Soups:**

* Gazpacho (Spanish)
* Minestrone (Italian)
* Greek lemon soup (avgolemono)
* French onion soup
* Turkish lentil soup

**Stews:**

* Beef tagine (Moroccan)
* Lamb stew (Greek)
* Spanish paella
* Italian osso buco
* French cassoulet

**Hot Drinks:**

* Turkish coffee
* Greek coffee
* Arabic coffee
* Salep (Turkish)
* Anise tea
